title: SENSATION 2007 ISO
description:
SENSATION
The Worlds Leading Dance Event


Thousands of people stepped into a magical world in the Amsterdam Arena and gathered underneath the "Oak of Love" on July 7, 2007

This DVD brings to life the sights and sounds of the seventh edition of sensation, "The Worlds&#039;Leading Dance Event". Embark on a journey of discovery of the world&#039;s top DJs, top acts,tempting creatures and special effects that all combine to create the best party on the planet
Plus enjoy the added bonus of the 30 minutes of megamix highlights, all the sensation anthems from 2000 onwards and exclusive and never-shown-before footage of the 2006 dreamshow
